Cyberpunk style: A towering holographic lock mechanism floats above a rain-slicked cityscape at night, its translucent blue structure constantly shifting and rebuilding itself from digital fragments. Below, a lone figure in a long coat stands at a terminal, watching as ethereal key-shaped data streams spiral upward and dissolve into the neon-lit clouds. The lock's core pulses with energy, showing layers of concentric rings that rotate independently, each ring displaying flowing circuit patterns. Steam rises from street vents, catching the magenta and cyan glow from massive advertising screens on distant skyscrapers. The scene emphasizes impermanence and controlled chaos—components materializing and dematerializing in an endless cycle of creation and destruction, symbolizing ephemeral authentication systems that exist only for a moment before vanishing into digital mist.
